Module:
JUnit 5 - Basic Testing

Description:
This repository contains the solutions for the JUnit 5 Basic Testing exercises from the Cognizant Digital Nurture 5.0 Java Full Stack Engineer (DN 5.0 Java FSE) program.

Each exercise has been implemented as an independent Maven project using JUnit 5. The objective of these exercises is to understand the fundamentals of unit testing, assertions, test organization, and the JUnit testing lifecycle.

