Exercises Completed
---------------------------------------------------------

Exercise 1 - Setting Up JUnit
--------------------------------
Objective:
- Created a Maven Java project.
- Configured JUnit 5 using Maven.
- Created and executed the first JUnit test class.
- Verified successful JUnit setup.

Files:
- pom.xml
- SampleTest.java

